<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Access Granted</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f5f7fa; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.08); }
    .header { background: #0ea5e9; padding: 32px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; }
    .body { padding: 32px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6; }
    .card { background: #f0f9ff; border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9; border-radius: 4px; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0; }
    .card p { margin: 4px 0; font-size: 14px; }
    .card strong { color: #0369a1; }
    .footer { background: #f9fafb; padding: 24px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; }
    .footer a { color: #6b7280; }
    .badge { display: inline-block; background: #d1fae5; color: #065f46; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸ”“ New Access Granted</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Hi <strong>{{patientName}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>A healthcare provider has been granted access to your medical records. Here are the details:</p>

      <div class="card">
        <p><strong>Provider:</strong> {{granteeName}}</p>
        {{#if granteeSpecialty}}
        <p><strong>Specialty:</strong> {{granteeSpecialty}}</p>
        {{/if}}
        <p><strong>Record:</strong> {{recordTitle}}</p>
        {{#if recordType}}
        <p><strong>Type:</strong> {{recordType}}</p>
        {{/if}}
        <p><strong>Granted on:</strong> {{grantedAt}}</p>
      </div>

      <p>If you did not authorize this access or believe it was granted in error, please review your access settings immediately.</p>

      <p style="text-align:center; margin-top: 32px;">
        <a href="{{appUrl}}/access" style="background:#0ea5e9;color:#fff;padding:12px 28px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">
          Review Access Permissions
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>You received this notification because you have an active HealthRecord account.</p>
      <p><a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe from email notifications</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
